    {
      "Text": "Security update for shim",
      "Title": "Topic",
      "Type": "Summary"
    },
    {
      "Text": "This update for shim fixes the following issues:\n\n- Update to the unified shim binary for SBAT support (bsc#1182057)\n  + Merged EKU codesign check (bsc#1177315)\n- shim-install: Always assume 'removable' for Azure to avoid the endless reset loop (bsc#1185464).\n",
      "Title": "Details",
      "Type": "General"
    },
